channel.title: Got my server onto my Ip
channel.description: So i got it put on my ip as several guides had instructed, no errors loading up the server. But when I go to log in I get the error, [Java] Java.net.connectException: Connection refused: connect. I've done everything by the guide not sure if this is something on my half like maby security settings or firewall maby?
